com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities

Class BulkAdGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkAdGroup

  • public class BulkAdGroup
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents an Ad Group.

    This class exposes the setAdGroup(com.microsoft.bingads.campaignmanagement.AdGroup) and getAdGroup() that can be used to read and write fields of the Ad Group record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Ad Group at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=511537.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
